Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们接下来去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐　这怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小甘　表情真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}※浓缩洋葱精华2倍刺激中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？　刚才那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,@#￥%…　是…有原…因的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全听不清你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定了　就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,0:00:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定什么了...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是鬼屋哦　哥哥～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　那个我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ｌｅｔ'ｓ　哥哥　ｈｏ～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊　等　等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种孩子气的游戏　我早就不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　孩子气？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:01:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游王子竟然说出这种话...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以　没　没什么兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的　讴歌姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的鬼屋超级逼真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.39,0:01:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说卖点就是恐怖程度连大人都会吓得赤脚逃跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ｌｅｔ'ｓ　裘可！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来　讴歌姐姐也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道游王子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今水枪喷汁作战失败
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把赌注押在「恐惧」这种感情上 很有一试的价值
