Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从一开始就没有在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是人造的　放心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　不过…
