Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游王子　冷静点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在倒是能拍到游王子的哭脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真　真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　游王子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂～　游王子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游王子　没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背背
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘛　我要背背
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏　背背　我要背背
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经超过孩子气的次元了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游王子　贴太紧的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我讴歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我讴歌！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊　这　这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讴　讴歌～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事　没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶　到底哪里离出口近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择吧
